characters.name: Todd Chavez
quotes: Fool me once, fool me twice, fool me chicken soup with rice
Sometimes I just feel like my whole life is just a series of loosely related, wacky misadventures...
Can we return to the surface? All my favorite clouds are up there.

characters.name: Bojack Horseman
characters.occupation: Actor; Owner of the Restaurant Elephante
quotes: Y'know, sometimes I feel like I was born with a leak, and any goodness I started with just slowly spilled out of me, and now it's all gone and I'll never get it back in me. It's too late.
Life is a series of closing doors, isn't it?
CAN WE PLEASE GET SOME ALCOHOL INTO MY MOUTH?!

characters.name: Princess Carolyn
quotes: My life is a mess right now and I compulsively take care of other people when I don't know how to take care of myself.
Stop pissing off the orphans. A lot of them grow up to be serial killers.

characters.name: Diane Nguyen
quotes: That’s the thing. I don’t think I believe in deep down. I kind of think all you are is just the things that you do.

characters.name: Mr. Peanutbutter
quotes: The universe is a cruel, uncaring void. The key to being happy isn't a search for meaning. It's to just keep yourself busy with unimportant nonsense, and eventually, you'll be dead.

characters.name: Jogging Baboon
quotes: It gets easier... Every day it gets a little easier... But you gotta do it every day — that’s the hard part. But it does get easier.
